attributionInfo.brokerName: KELLER WILLIAMS ISLAND LIFE REAL ESTATE

data.description: Impressive 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home with attached 2 Car Garage located in THE HAMMOCKS OF WEST PORT. New construction in 2022, the Drexel C3 model by Maronda Homes. This light and bright home features an open and split bedroom floor plan with Great Room, well appointed Kitchen, Inside Laundry and large screened rear porch. The Kitchen is open to the Great Room and offers granite counters, wood cabinets, stainless appliances, double pantry closet. Great storage and counter space. There is an island with double sink, breakfast bar and dishwasher. The nearby Laundry Room has a washer and dryer hookup. The spacious Great Room features lake views, tile flooring, high ceilings and sliding glass doors to the screened lanai.  The Master Bedroom suite has a walk in closet and private bathroom with dual sinks and large walk in shower with seat. There are two additional good sized bedrooms with double closets. One of the bedrooms is currently being used as a fitness room. The guest bathroom has a tub/shower combo. The screened lanai/porch offers lake views and plenty of space for grilling and relaxing. This screened lanai is oversized - it was extended the full legth of the back of the home. Other features include tile flooring throughout the home, crown molding, hich ceilings and hurricane shutters. West Port is located near Centennial Park which offers public amenities including an Aquatic Center (where you can swim for a small annual fee), fitness classes, pickleball, walking trails, 18 hole disc golf course, volleyball courts, programs, events and more! The Charlotte Sports Park is close by where the Tampa Bay Rays will be returning for spring training in 2024. West Port is also minutes from shopping, dining, medical care, entertainment, I-75 and more. This home is perfect for year round living, seasonal use or rental investment. A beautiful home in a great community!
